Entitas dan Atribut
**User **

user_id (Primary Key)
username (Unique)
password (Hash)
role (ENUM: 'dosen', 'mahasiswa')
created_at (Timestamp)
updated_at (Timestamp)
Dosen

dosen_id (Primary Key, Foreign Key to User.user_id)
nama (String)
nip (String, Unique)
email (String, Unique)
jurusan (String)
Mahasiswa

mahasiswa_id (Primary Key, Foreign Key to User.user_id)
nama (String)
nim (String, Unique)
email (String, Unique)
jurusan (String)


